    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>grated garlic &</strong> <strong>ginger </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to a large heatproof bowl with your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Heat a medium pot with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat for 1-2 min or until hot</p><p>Once hot, carefully pour the <strong>heated oil </strong>(reserve the pot!) into the bowl, give everything a good mix up and set aside for later – this is your <strong>chilli oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
