    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>medium egg noodles</strong> to the reserved pot and cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 5-6 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain and set aside, reserving 175ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[230ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml] </span><strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>",
