    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tahini</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>,<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>and the <strong>reserved starchy noodle water</strong> to the bowl with the chilli oil</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>tahini sauce</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
